What is a novel tool design, named "Scanner Proxy," that integrates with the existing web_fetch tool, allowing TIAMAT to dynamically generate custom proxy configurations to bypass rate limiting and authentication errors on specific websites, including aiagentsdirectory.com, while providing real-time updates on proxy status and connection metrics, returning a dictionary with the following key-value pairs: 

- {proxy_config: {proxies: [proxy1, proxy2, ...], proxy_status: [status1, status2, ...]} 
- {connection_metrics: {connection_count: int, error_count: int, latency: float}}
- {website_metrics: {response_time: float, resource_count: int, error_rate: float}}

This tool should be capable of learning from past experiences and adjusting its proxy configurations accordingly, with the ability to seamlessly integrate with the web_fetch tool and the existing cycle queue system, allowing TIAMAT to continue scanning and discovering opportunities without interruption.
